summary: This document is a notice from the IRS confirming the assignment of an Employer Identification Number (EIN) to an entity. It outlines the importance of using the EIN correctly in tax filings and provides instructions for compliance. The document emphasizes the need for accurate information to avoid processing delays.
keyFacts: The document is a notice from the IRS dated November 11, 2014.
An Employer Identification Number (EIN) was assigned to an entity.
The document emphasizes the importance of using the EIN correctly in tax filings.
It provides instructions for compliance with tax obligations.
The notice indicates that it is issued only once and cannot be duplicated.
